IT team to build and maintain applications for Indices business which builds indexes across asset classes like fixed income bonds and leverage loans, 
QIS indices like equity, commodities, fx

We have feeds that extracts data like prices, static instrument strucures from various external and internal sources. 
The extracted data is transformed and loaded to database. 
Index calculation engine uses the data to calculate analytics. The analytics are aggregated at index level using SQL analitical services. 
The data is then made available to clients via feeds and external facing web portal. 

